# Regression: a list literal whose body contains an overloaded operation
# that fans out (here `:0:` on the still-generic `map.` element, narrowed
# by `toFixed`) must reconcile the branches and produce `[str]`. The list
# literal previously evaluated its body with a flat loop that ignored the
# branch fan-out, collapsing `[ a b ]` to a bare scalar and tripping
# `tjoin` with "expected [str], got str".
[ [1.5 2.0] [3.25 4.0] ] map.
    row!
    [ @row :0: 2 toFixed   @row :1: 1 toFixed ]
    tjoin
end
uw
